original_text: And the children of Israel did eat manna forty years, until they came to a land inhabited; they did eat manna, until they came unto the borders of the land of Canaan.
korean_text: 사람이 사는 땅에 이르기까지 이스라엘 자손이 사십 년 동안 만나를 먹었으니 곧 가나안 땅 접경에 이르기까지 그들이 만나를 먹었더라

sentences.original_text: And the children of Israel did eat manna
until they came to a land inhabited
sentences.korean_translation: 그들이 사람이 사는 땅에 이를 때까지

sentences.original_text: until they came unto the borders of the land of Canaan
